									{
										"data": [
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "AnimationTags"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[Isobel] performs spell [Player][Party] react to being magic protected <Greg>"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "Attitude"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Default"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "|Casts 'Protection from Good and Evil', but modified with Selunite (moon) magic to protect against the Shadowcurse specifically. Isobel can use the planned animations for this spell cinematically, or something bespoke as best fits the scene. (lighting tests in progree for clouds revealing the moon)\r\n\r\nWe see every present party member  take on a moon-like effect as a result of being targeted with the spell, which then fades as though absorbed by each of them. This gives them a special in-game status to protect them from the curse|"
												}
											},
