					"type": 23,
					"value": "Isobel is in her room re-casting the spell that is protecting the inn. After she spots you, she gives you information about Ketheric and a spell to protect you from the shadowcurse.\r\n\r\nAfter Isobel gives this information, she is interrupted by the Absolute-tadpoled Flaming Fist, who attempts to kidnap her."
